{"tid":1469660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地香港人 未驚過呀 有咩風波拆得散我地？","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:51:08.000Z","uid":55493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"697753de570be166845b9cdb9cabeac14904632f","tid":1469660,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"我地香港人嗌兩聲we are Hong Kong<br />\n個心即刻定晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政權？冇撚驚過你呀<br />\n<br />\n我地團結 勇毅 無野驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係香港人 我地香港人 驚你老母閪"},{"pid":"b0bd8ba2483975a2f54b86c8a99743cd90957064","tid":1469660,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ba82411a6237af22c9445fd669779bf88ac8a2","tid":1469660,"uid":